sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Aluno
    participant AL as adaptive-learning-service
    participant DB as RDS Postgres
    participant CACHE as ElastiCache Redis
    participant EB as EventBridge
    participant Q as SQS recommendation-jobs
    participant INT as integrations-service (Lambda)
    participant IA as Motor IA externo
    participant DLQ as SQS DLQ

    Aluno->>AL: GET /trilha/atual
    AL->>CACHE: get(recommendations:alunoId)

    alt cache hit
        CACHE-->>AL: trilha cacheada
        AL-->>Aluno: 200 OK (trilha)
    else cache miss
        AL->>DB: SELECT progresso
        AL-->>Aluno: 200 OK (trilha padrao + flag "atualizando")
        AL->>Q: enqueue RecommendationJob(alunoId, cid=Y)
    end

    rect rgb(255,233,214)
    note over Q,INT: Processamento assincrono
    Q->>INT: trigger batch
    INT->>IA: POST /recommend(progresso)

    alt IA responde em < 8s
        IA-->>INT: recomendacoes
        INT->>EB: publica RecommendationReady
        EB->>AL: handler atualiza cache
        AL->>CACHE: SET recommendations:alunoId TTL=1h
    else IA falha ou timeout
        IA-->>INT: erro/timeout
        note over INT: retry 3x com backoff + jitter
        INT--xQ: nao apaga mensagem
        Q->>DLQ: apos 5 tentativas
        note over DLQ: alarme dispara, runbook secao 3
    end
    end

    note over Aluno,AL: Proxima visita do aluno encontra recomendacao no cache (eventually consistent)
